%% Data Flow Diagram - ODH Notebook Controller (kubeflow)
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>(Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Notebook as Notebook Container<br/>8888/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 1: Notebook Access WITH kube-rbac-proxy Authentication

    User->>Gateway: GET /notebook/{ns}/{name}<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS (service-ca cert)<br/>Bearer Token forwarded
    KRBP->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS<br/>Validate Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Auth Result (allow/deny)
    KRBP->>Notebook: Proxy request<br/>HTTP/8888, plaintext (localhost)<br/>X-Auth-Request-User/Groups headers
    Notebook-->>KRBP: Response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response (HTTPS)
    Gateway-->>User: Response (HTTPS)

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 2: Notebook Access WITHOUT kube-rbac-proxy

    User->>Gateway: GET /notebook/{ns}/{name}<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>Notebook: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8888, plaintext
    Notebook-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: Response (HTTPS)

    participant Controller as ODH Notebook<br/>Controller
    participant Webhook as Mutating Webhook<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over K8sAPI,Controller: Flow 3: Controller Reconciliation

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch Notebook CRs<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS, SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Notebook event
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute (central ns)<br/>HTTPS/443
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ReferenceGrant (user ns)<br/>HTTPS/443
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy (user ns)<br/>HTTPS/443
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create kube-rbac-proxy Service/ConfigMap/CRB<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over K8sAPI,Webhook: Flow 4: Webhook Mutation

    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-notebook-v1<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS (service-ca cert)
    Webhook->>K8sAPI: Lookup ImageStream tags<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS, SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>Webhook: ImageStream data
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Notebook<br/>(+sidecar, +CA certs, +volumes)

    Note over Controller,K8sAPI: Flow 5: Elyra Pipeline Secret Reconciliation

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Read DSPA CR (notebook ns)<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS, SA Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Read Gateway CR (openshift-ingress)<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS, SA Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update ds-pipeline-config Secret<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS, SA Token
